articles.author: Ben Gardner
articles.title: Ian Bell: Despite defeat, England have psychological hold over scared Aussies - Wisden
articles.description: Despite defeat in the Ashes opener at Edgbaston, England are “inside the heads” of Australia’s Test team, according to former England batter Ian Bell.
articles.content:
